SERVER CREATION

basic commands
 1) create package.json -npm init
 2) create nodemodules
       install express - npm i express

 b) Basic steps

 1) creating a folder (bankServer)
 2) create a package.json file (npm init)
 3) create a nodemodules file (npm express)
 4) create index.js  file
 5) import express inside index.js
 6) create app using express
 7) set up port number
 8) Resolving Http requests
 9) install nodemon - npm i -g nodemon
 10) http response code
               1xx -information
               2xx- succesfull
               3xx -redirection
               4xx -client error
               5xx -server error

 11)JWT token -Authenticate
 To check  login or not?

 login-----token generate------>client------req to deposite+token-------->server  token check?

 Install JWT  - jsonwebtoken
    -npm i jsonwebtoken


To generate a new JWT Token - sign()

12) Middleware -To verify the token

-it comes in the middle of the request and response
-it also provides access to many function 
        1.Application-level middleware
        -For Entire appliction

        2.Router-level middleware
        -To verify the token/-To validate the token-verify()
13 Database integration 
1) Install mongoose -npm i mongoose (for connecting mongodb and nodejs)
2) DB connect via mongoose
3) create a model using mongoose

14) asynchronous function -then()
   1) resolving state -then()
   2)rejection state -catch()

15) CORS -Cross origin resource sharing
install cors-npm i cors
 